ia Rodrigo Lacy Guts Instagram" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/newjeans-njz-hanni-cover-olivia-rodrigo-lacy-guts-instagram.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/newjeans-njz-hanni-cover-olivia-rodrigo-lacy-guts-instagram-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/newjeans-njz-hanni-cover-olivia-rodrigo-lacy-guts-instagram-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/newjeans-njz-hanni-cover-olivia-rodrigo-lacy-guts-instagram-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/newjeans-njz-hanni-cover-olivia-rodrigo-lacy-guts-instagram-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/newjeans-njz-hanni-cover-olivia-rodrigo-lacy-guts-instagram-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> K-Pop Girl Group <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/newjeans">Newjeans</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-unveil-new-group-name-amidst-hybe-and-ador-feud-3835798">也称为NJZ</a> ）的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hanni">Hanni</a>分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">Olivia Rodrigo</a>的“ Lacy”的新声音封面。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ador-hybe-feud-timeline-story-3754759">Newjeans vs Hybe：事件的全面时间表</a></strong></li></ul><p>3月3日，纽吉恩斯（Newjeans）的汉尼（Hanni）上传了自己表演“蕾丝”（Lacy）的视频 -<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/olivia-rodrigo-guts-album-review-vampire-3493907">罗德里戈（Rodrigo）的2023专辑“ Guts”（Guts）</a>的曲目 - 乐队的独立Instagram页面。长达两分钟的剪辑以K-Pop偶像演唱时弹奏吉他，忠于原始乐器的声音吉他。</p><p> <em>“蕾丝，哦，花边，皮肤像泡芙糕点一样 /你不是地狱这一面最甜蜜的东西吗？ /亲爱的天使蕾丝（Angel Lacy），雏菊（Daisies）的眼睛 /我曾经告诉过你我做得不好吗？”</em>她克罗恩斯。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DGvAOKlSqDH/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; borde