babymonster-batter-up-review-swing-and-a-miss-3549523">他们的首张单曲“ Batter Up”</a>以及热门单曲“ Sheesh”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babymonster-2025-hello-monsters-world-tour-cities-dates-tickets-more-3813574">Babymonster帖子添加了新的北美停靠站，到2025年“ Hello Monsters”世界巡回演唱</a>会首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
